videos.description: QB David Blough finds WR Terry Wright in the corner of the end zone, giving Purdue a 7-3 lead.
videos.headline: Boilermakers go on top with 12-yard TD pass

videos.description: QB Drew Lock zips a pass to WR Johnathon Johnson in the back of the end zone to make it 10-7 Tigers.
videos.headline: Missouri answers with 21-yard TD

videos.description: DB Cam Hilton snuffs out the fake-reverse and leaps to make an athletic interception, leading to a Missouri field goal.
videos.headline: Tigers spoil trick-play attempt with INT

videos.description: QB Drew Lock is on target to WR Jalen Knox, who outruns the defense and takes it all the way to make it 20-10 Tigers.
videos.headline: Missouri extends lead with 59-yard TD pass

videos.description: Johnathon Johnson makes an acrobatic 30-yard reception, setting up another Tigers touchdown.
videos.headline: Missouri WR lays out to make incredible diving catch

videos.description: QB David Blough fires one to TE Brycen Hopkins, who comes down with it and trims the Boilermakers' deficit to 27-24.
videos.headline: Purdue scores before halftime with 3-yard TD pass

videos.description: Drew Lock keeps it himself for an 8-yard touchdown run, breaking the tie and making it 34-27 Tigers.
videos.headline: Missouri breaks tie with QB run

videos.description: WR Rondale Moore is gifted with a deflected pass, turning it into a 74-yard reception to set up a critical Purdue touchdown.
videos.headline: Purdue WR in right spot at right time for huge reception
